    <description>Calculate the terminated employee Group Sub group. (US382794) - Fix tenure calculation and set correct group &amp; subgroup if an employee&apos;s termination date and hire date are the same (DE103811)
US400995 || CTB | Add Nebula logging on record creation, deletion and updates - Employee</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>EndDateTime</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>TEXT({!$Flow.CurrentDateTime})</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>FlowName</name>
